show.description: Betrayed by love, mocked by the elite, and dismissed as a loser, George returns, not to beg, but to rise. As secrets unravel and power games ignite, he claims his destiny as the Dragon King. Ready to witness how revenge fuels the rise of a legend? Watch Now.
